assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Nippon Grande Co.,Ltd. operates as a real estate development company in Japan. The company engages in the design, planning, construction supervision, diagnosis, supervision, development, and sale of lots and apartments, as well as lots of detached houses. It is also involved in the real estate trading and brokerage activities; management, operation, and brokerage of office buildings; renovation and renovation work contract, as well as interior coordination activities; and real estate securitization business covering real estate planning, development, and consulting activities. In addition, the company offers type 2 financial instruments; provides real estate investment advisory services; engages in the planning, design, and operation services of housing for elderly people; sells charcoal power clean system patent enforcement rights; and operates in the general insurance agency and advertising businesses. Nippon Grande Co.,Ltd. was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Sapporo City, Japan.
